OL,3,CThe chancellor's choice between
OL,4,CNational Insurance and income tax cuts
OL,6,FMy hunch, as I said , is he'll do a
OL,7,Fpenny off each. But as of now, that is
OL,8,Fhow it smells rather than what I know.
OL,10,FWhat I know is that 2p in the pound is
OL,11,Fcoming off these taxes on income in
OL,12,Fsome combination or other.
OL,14,FTorsten Bell from the think tank the
OL,15,FResolution Foundation said in a post
OL,16,Fon X that Jeremy Hunt is "choosing a
OL,17,Ftotally new approach to the shape of
OL,18,Ftax policy".
