OL,3,CThe chancellor's choice between
OL,4,CNational Insurance and income tax cuts
OL,6,FHe compares Mr Hunt's tax policy to
OL,7,Fthat of former Chancellor George
OL,8,FOsborne, saying: "I think everyone who
OL,9,Fworks on tax policy will recognise
OL,10,Fthat Jeremy Hunt's is by far the
OL,11,Fbetter tax reform strategy - whatever
OL,12,Fthey think about whether the tax cuts
OL,13,Fcan be afforded in the current
OL,14,Fclimate."
