OL,3,CThe chancellor's choice between
OL,4,CNational Insurance and income tax cuts
OL,6,FThe distributional impact, i.e winners
OL,7,Fand losers, are interesting. According
OL,8,Fto the Resolution Foundation, those
OL,9,Fearning up to #19,000 would be net
OL,10,Flosers because of freezing of
OL,11,Fthresholds.
OL,13,FThose earning just under #50,000 would
OL,14,Fbe biggest winners, with net gain of
OL,15,F#1200.
OL,17,FAbove that threshold the benefits
OL,18,Fshrink in relative terms. And remember
OL,19,Fthe NI cut hands zilch to pensioners
OL,20,Fand those with so-called unearned
OL,21,Fincome.
